      "message": "wallet: use 'maxfeerate' startup option in wallet\n\nThis commit updates all instances where maxtxfee is utilized to check if transaction\nfee rate exceeds the maximum fee rate.\n\nInstead, the startup option maxfeerate is now used to determine the\nmaximum fee rate.\nThis is achieved by assigning the\nuser-passed maxfeerate value to the wallet's max_tx_fee_rate.\n\nThis adds the default behavior of maxfeerate to the wallet,\nif maxfeerate is 0 wallet will now accept any feerate.",
